  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function set_shininess(shininess: Number(gfloat)): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_pipeline_set_shininess()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Sets the shininess of the pipeline, in the standard OpenGL lighting
model, which determines the size of the specular highlights. A
higher <code>shininess</code> will produce smaller highlights which makes the
object appear more shiny.</p>  <p>The default value is 0.0</p>
  <p>Since 2.0</p>
<terms>
